After downloading these 95 files, how do i get them to play and how do i join them into 1 single DVD? Help out!

orlash: 

Just use some good compression software like Winrar to decompress them. Unpack the file ending with .00 or .01 (for example) and the rest will fix itself. After the program is done you'll end up with a single file, probably with a .img extension. If you can't do anything with that just rename the extension to .iso and then mount it or burn it as an image, depending on what you prefer.
